'''内耳'''（{{lang-en|Inner ear}}）是[[耳|耳]]的解剖结构的一部分，含有人体[[听觉|听觉]]和[[平衡觉|平衡觉]]的[[感受器|感受器]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Overview of the Inner Ear - Ear, Nose, and Throat Disorders|url=https://www.merckmanuals.com/home/ear,-nose,-and-throat-disorders/inner-ear-disorders/overview-of-the-inner-ear|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=Merck Manuals Consumer Version|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323231710/https://www.merckmanuals.com/home/ear,-nose,-and-throat-disorders/inner-ear-disorders/overview-of-the-inner-ear}}</ref>。内耳处于[[颞骨|颞骨]]空腔中，其最主要的结构是[[骨迷路|骨迷路]]，由'''[[前庭系统|前庭系统]]'''和'''[[耳蜗|耳蜗]]'''构成<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Inner ear and balance|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/dizziness/multimedia/inner-ear-and-balance/img-20006286|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=Mayo Clinic|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421183317/https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/dizziness/multimedia/inner-ear-and-balance/img-20006286}}</ref>。内耳连接着[[前庭耳蜗神经|前庭耳蜗神经]]，其中[[前庭神经|前庭神经]]传递平衡觉信息、[[耳蜗神经|耳蜗神经]]传递听觉信息<ref name=":0" />。

== 结构 ==

=== 前庭系统 ===
[[前庭系统|前庭系统]]是[[平衡觉|平衡觉]]的末梢器官，负责对头部的线性[[加速度|加速度]]和[[角加速度|角加速度]]的传感。前庭系统内包括[[半规管|半规管]]，连接着[[前庭神经|前庭神经]]<ref name=":0" />。

前庭系统的异常可导致[[头晕|头晕]]、[[眩暈_(醫學)|眩晕]]等问题<ref name=":0" />。

=== 耳蜗 ===
[[耳蜗|耳蜗]]是听觉的末梢器官，致力于[[听觉|听觉]]，负责将来自[[外耳|外耳]]和[[中耳|中耳]]的机械[[振动|振动]]（即[[声音|声音]]）转换为神经信号。耳蜗中的[[柯蒂氏器|柯蒂氏器]]负责转换声压模式为电信号，然后通过[[聽覺神經|听觉神经]]（[[耳蜗神经|耳蜗神经]]）传递给大脑<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":02">{{Cite book|chapter=Anatomy, Head and Neck, Ear Organ of Corti|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK538335/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=30855919|first=Hunter J.|last=White|first2=Muhammad|last2=Helwany|first3=Diana C.|last3=Peterson|access-date=2021-03-13|archive-date=2021-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214202616/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK538335/}}</ref>。

耳蜗的异常导致[[感觉神经性耳聋|感觉神经性耳聋]]等问题<ref name=":0" />。

